From,their,site,Convio,is,an,Internet,software,and,services,company,that,provides,online,Constituent,Relationship,Management,eCRM,solutions,for,nonprofit,organizations,As,a,trusted,Internet,partner,for,more,than,organizations,The,Constituent,Management,API,is,a,REST,based,API,allowing,method,invocation,over,the,Internet,using,HTTP,POST,requests,The,API,communicates,directly,with,the,Convio,Constituent,database